    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a suspension that is beginning to feel soft. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and a few non-functional plastic trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional car who doesn't mind putting in a little work to freshen it up.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
