      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard that warrants the 'mint' designation. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and a pristine interior that retains its original luster. Meticulously preserved and mechanically peerless, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector to acquire an automotive asset of the highest caliber.",
