      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered since day one, always garage-kept and kept sparkling clean. You won't find a single blemish on it. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next home. I'm sad to see it go, but I know you're going to love it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 43500.0,
